How to Install phonegap-plugin-menu
===================================

Copy Files
----------

Copy all files except `INSTALL` to your iOS project.
The directory structure of the files is important.

Update PhoneGap.plist
---------------------

Add the following feature element to `ProjectName/PhoneGap.plist`:

    <key>com.phonegap.menu.context</key>
    <string>PGTabBar</string>

    <key>com.phonegap.menu.context.command</key>
    <string>PGTabBarItem</string>

    <key>com.phonegap.menu.toolbar</key>
    <string>PGToolBar</string>

    <key>com.phonegap.menu.toolbar.command</key>
    <string>PGToolBarItem</string>
